This app is to get the temprature of the given city.
There are some steps to follow to run this app:

1. Clone the repo.
2. install the requirements. (wait...)
3. create the .env file outside of the app directory.
4. sign up for the "https://www.weatherapi.com".
5. get URL & API_key from the site.
6. The URL is have used is "http://api.weatherapi.com/v1/current.json" (please use the same)
7. create the API_key & define these in .evn file.
8. Then create the venv & install the requirements.
9. At the end run the app.py file with python app.py.

Thanks....
